    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司 1400 亿美元的现金储备预示着股东回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/big-tech-s-140-billion-cash-haul-points-to-shareholder-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大型科技公司带来的现金比以往任何时候都多，这促使该集团向股东返还资金，并可能为已经使该集团大部分股票进入创纪录水平的涨势增添动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/big-tech-s-140-billion-cash-haul-points-to-shareholder-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:15:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
