      <title>安哥拉计划今年该国最大电信公司首次公开募股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/angola-eyes-ipo-of-country-s-biggest-telecoms-company-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安哥拉计划于2024年对该国最大的电信公司Unitel进行首次公开​​募股，因为由于美国降息的预期，今年对风险较高的新兴市场资产的需求预计将增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/angola-eyes-ipo-of-country-s-biggest-telecoms-company-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 15:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
